@{
    ViewBag.Title = "How Trim Works";
}
<h2>@ViewBag.Title.</h2>
<h3>@ViewBag.Message</h3>

<p>Trim Tailor – A tech enabled company providing a tailoring service that seamlessly links into the lives of consumers. Customers can create a profile with their dimensions, which will allow them to order from any online vendor, have it tailored by Trim, then delivered to their doorstep. This process removes the time and effort that has previously gone into perfectly fitting clothes; in addition, it makes custom tailoring available to people in wider geographic demographics. </p>
